  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ModuleHandleWin32</TypeRef> class is an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IModuleHandle">IModuleHandle</PageRef> implementation.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Availability: Windows. This type is used when <TypeRef>COBALT_RENDERER_WIN32_SUPPORT</TypeRef> is enabled and the implementation is compiled on Windows.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
